          "id": "C01_002",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "character": "qingmiao",
          "expression": "happy",
          "name": "青苗",
          "text": "（从背囊里探出头）终于到了！主人，这里草药的气息好浓！往南走——青苗感觉到了！",
          "avatar": "qingmiao.png",
          "nextDelay": 500
        },
        {
          "id": "C01_003",
          "type": "tutorial",
